              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27183644/" class="">自由主义</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49186147/" class=" " title="颜">颜</a>
                (鞋写)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27183644">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">国家是一种必要的罪恶：如无必要，它的权力不应增加</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-06-20 14:30</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                国家是一种必要的罪恶：如无必要，它的权力不应增加
